Package net.officefloor.web.resource.spi

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileCache
    Cache of files.
    FileCacheFactory
    Factory for the creation of a new FileCache.
    FileCacheService
    ServiceFactory for the FileCacheFactory.
    FileCacheServiceContext
    Context for the FileCacheService.
    ResourceSystem
    Underlying system to the HttpResourceStore.
    ResourceSystemContext
    Context for the ResourceSystem.
    ResourceSystemFactory
    Service for the creation of a ResourceSystem.
    ResourceSystemService
    ServiceFactory interface for providing a ResourceSystemFactory.
    ResourceTransformer
    Transforms resource instances.
    ResourceTransformerContext
    Context for the ResourceTransformer.
    ResourceTransformerFactory
    Factory to create the ResourceTransformer.
    ResourceTransformerService
    ServiceFactory for the ResourceTransformerFactory.
